menon: gone'><font color='#000000'>ἀπολλυμένων</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:ἀπολλυμένων' title='6) gone'><font color='#000000'> gone</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:χάριτι' title='chariti: gratitude'><font color='#000000'>χάριτι</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:χάριτι' title='7) gratitude'><font color='#000000'>→</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:καὶ' title='kai: and'><font color='#000000'>καὶ</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:καὶ' title='8) and'><font color='#000000'> and</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῷ' title='to: to the'><font color='#000000'>τῷ</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῷ' title='9) to the; by the; in the'><font color='#000000'>by</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:γιγνώσκειν' title='gignoskein: knowing'><font color='#000000'>γιγνώσκειν</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:γιγνώσκειν' title='10) knowing'><font color='#000000'> knowing</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:ὅτι' title='oti: that'><font color='#000000'>ὅτι</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:ὅτι' title='11) that'><font color='#000000'> that</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index